  the  hon  minister  has presented  a  very  important  bill  in  this  house    this  is  a  very  important amendment  as  far  as  this  country  is  concerned    investment  is  required  for installation of such nuclear plants in the country and this bill fulfills this objective  nuclear  plants  are  totally  safe    and  the  nuclear  power  plant  of  tarapur  is  an example to support this  so there is no need of being in fear due to such plants  